Automated Threat Intelligence Enrichment

Before escalation, incidents should be enriched with context (hash, domain, IP). XSOAR can query multiple TI sources (VirusTotal, MISP, Palo Alto Autofocus, Recorded Future).

### Flow (ASCII Diagram)

+-------------------------+
| IOC Detected (alert)    |
+-------------------------+
           |
           v
+-------------------------+
| Automation Trigger      |
| (IOC extraction)        |
+-------------------------+
           |
           v
+-------------------------+
| Threat Intel Queries    |
| - VirusTotal            |
| - MISP                  |
| - Recorded Future       |
+-------------------------+
           |
           v
+-------------------------+
| Aggregate Reputation    |
| + Confidence Scoring    |
+-------------------------+
           |
           v
+-------------------------+
| Update Incident         |
| (add TI context)        |
+-------------------------+

**Benefit:** eliminates manual copy/paste lookups, ensures consistent enrichment.
